1:1 COMMENT "# autoproject.z -- Implicit protocol projection at call sites"
1:62 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# When a function parameter's declared type is a protocol (or"
3:62 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# facet), passing a concrete value that conforms to the protocol is"
4:68 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# accepted without an explicit `protocol.borrow from: x` /"
5:59 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# `protocol.take from: x` wrapper. The compiler synthesises the"
6:64 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# projection automatically, picking `borrow` by default and `take`"
7:67 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# when the parameter is annotated `.take`."
8:43 EOL "\n"
9:1 EOL "\n"
